dct_description_sm: Traced from and showing part of the information on map entitled Map of Essex County, New Jersey, with names of property holders showing portions of southern Essex County which are now in Union County. In addition to local roads, map indicates mountain ranges.
Two significant portions of map torn away. Major discoloration from adhesive tape marks.
